description: On this CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, TSM Myth  comes on as a guest to talk about  a lot of things including the latest on Daequan and Hamlinz disappearance from the spotlight, challenging Shroud and Symfuhny to a boxing match, why he quit Fortnite, ranked Apex Legends' popularity, and more!
